<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EcoMind</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8a2be2, #ff69b4, #1e90ff);
        margin: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: white;
        display: flex;
        border-radius: 20px;
      }
      .image-container {
        background: url("https://img.freepik.com/free-vector/liquid-style-background_23-2148476933.jpg")
          no-repeat;
        background-size: auto 100%;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        height: 600px;
        width: 600px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      .image-contents {
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
        position: relative;
        left: -100%; /* Start off-screen to the left */
        opacity: 0; /* Initially invisible */
        animation: slideInFromLeft 0.5s forwards, fadeIn 1s forwards; /* Combine slide and fade animations */
      }

      @keyframes slideInFromLeft {
        0% {
          left: -100%; /* Start off-screen to the left */
        }
        100% {
          left: 0; /* Slide in to the left */
        }
      }

      @keyframes fadeIn {
        0% {
          opacity: 0; /* Start invisible */
        }
        100% {
          opacity: 1; /* Fade in to visible */
        }
      }
      .image-container > .image-contents > h3 {
        font-size: 20px;
        margin: 10;
      }
      .image-container > .image-contents > h1 {
        margin: 10;
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 35px;
      }
      .image-container > .image-contents > h1 > span {
        color: #007fc4;
      }
      .image-container > .image-contents > p {
        margin: 0px 50px;
        text-align: justify;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .login-container {
        padding: 50px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        position: relative;
        right: -100%;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: slideInFromRight 0.5s forwards, fadeIn 1s forwards;
      }

      @keyframes slideInFromRight {
        0% {
          right: -100%;
        }
        100% {
          right: 0;
        }
      }

      @keyframes fadeIn {
        0% {
          opacity: 0;
        }
        100% {
          opacity: 1;
        }
      }
      .login-container > h2 {
        font-size: 45px;
        color: #007fc4;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 50px;
      }
      .login-container > h3 {
        color: rgb(88, 86, 86);
        font-size: 18px;
        margin: 20px;
        margin-left: 0;
      }
      input {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      button {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 10px;
        background-color: #667eea;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background-color 0.3s;
      }
      button:hover {
        background-color: #764ba2;
      }
      h5 {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: end;
      }
      h5 > a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #667eea;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 15px;
      }
      .forgot-password {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 15px;
      }
      .forgot-password a {
        color: #667eea;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="image-container">
        <div class="image-contents">
          <h3>Nice to see you Again</h3>
          <h1>Welcome to Eco<span>Mind</span></h1>
          <p>
            where every thought finds its voice. Whether you're here to reflect,
            inspire, or connect with like-minded individuals, this platform is
            your canvas. Share your experiences, ideas, and musings in a space
            designed for genuine expression and meaningful conversations. Let
            your thoughts shape narratives, spark discussions, and foster
            understanding. Join us on a journey of discovery, where every
            perspective adds richness to our collective tapestry of thoughts.
            Embrace the power of sharing, because here, your voice matters.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="login-container">
        <h2>Login Here!</h2>
        <h3>Enter your Login Details:-</h3>
        <form method="post" action="/login/post">
          <input
            type="email"
            name="email"
            placeholder="Email"
            value="Arpit@gmail.com"
            required
          />
          <input
            type="password"
            name="password"
            placeholder="Password"
            value="Arpit"
            required
          />
          <h5><a href="#">Forgot password?</a></h5>

          <button type="submit">Log In</button>
        </form>
        <div class="forgot-password">
          <a href="/register">Don't have an account? Sign Up</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
